Favorite
Pinpoint
&nbsp;
Art
Leaders
Gallery
Art
Leaders
Gallery,
voted
“Michigan’s
Best
Fine
Art
Gallery”,
is
truly
a
treasure
to
behold.
In
Its
10,000
square
foot
showroom,
the
gallery
represents
high
quality
artwork
by
international,
national,
and
local
Michigan
artists,
as
well
as
emerging
new
talents
in
the
industry.
Favorite
Pinpoint
&nbsp;
Judy
Frankel
Antiques
With
her
exquisite
taste
and
keen
eye
for
European
style,
Judy
Frankel’s
name
has
been
synonymous
with
unique,
decorative
antiques
since
1991.
